00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:30,840
You even dare to say that you were self-reflecting

248
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:33,270
cultivating your mind, and haven't touched any wine!

249
00:20:33,270 --> 00:20:36,540
I think you were dancing happily at night and getting drunk!

250
00:20:36,540 --> 00:20:40,250
This wine has gotten so deep into your bones that you canâ€™t even hold a bowl of medicine properly.

251
00:20:40,250 --> 00:20:42,780
How do you still look like a Great Tang's Crown Prince?

252
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:46,660
How can you let me entrust Great Tang's future to you?

253
00:20:46,670 --> 00:20:48,600
Your Majesty is scolding me for my sake.

254
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:51,150
I do not dare to go against you. But if I do not explain myself,

255
00:20:51,150 --> 00:20:53,290
then I am afraid I would make Your Majesty ill again from anger.

256
00:20:53,290 --> 00:20:55,540
My hand was trembling because

257
00:20:56,680 --> 00:20:59,440
I have been copying scriptures every day.

258
00:21:02,630 --> 00:21:05,950
- Copying scriptures?
- I have been praying for Your Majesty's blessing,

259
00:21:05,950 --> 00:21:09,340
and pledged to Buddha a promise to copy 100 times the Diamond Sutra and the Earth Store Bodhisattva Sutra.

260
00:21:09,340 --> 00:21:11,410
I have not left the house at all,

261
00:21:11,410 --> 00:21:13,270
I totally focused on copying the scriptures

262
00:21:13,270 --> 00:21:16,020
so much that my hand is overused and its tendons are hurt,

263
00:21:16,020 --> 00:21:18,290
which caused my right hand

264
00:21:18,290 --> 00:21:22,340
to be unable to control itself and waver intensely. It is me who is useless.

265
00:21:24,740 --> 00:21:28,420
If you were concentrating on copying the scriptures, why did you smell of alcoholic on your body?

266
00:21:28,420 --> 00:21:30,730
My hand trembles and cannot grasp the brush.

267
00:21:30,730 --> 00:21:34,200
A'Sheng couldn't dissuade me,

268
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:37,560
so he found medicine wine to rub my hand.

269
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:39,930
I did not know that Your Majesty would ask me to come over,

270
00:21:39,930 --> 00:21:43,060
so I rubbed the medicine wine on my arm.

271
00:21:43,610 --> 00:21:45,450
Call for the imperial physician!

272
00:21:45,450 --> 00:21:47,510
I obey your order.

273
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:16,350
Eunuch Pan, please don't leave!

274
00:22:16,350 --> 00:22:18,540
[Hall of Immortal Dew]

275
00:22:18,540 --> 00:22:21,250
Your Highness, what are your orders?

276
00:22:21,250 --> 00:22:23,150
There are numerous imperial physicians.

277
00:22:23,150 --> 00:22:26,830
But I only trust Physician Zong's medical skills and moral qualities.

278
00:22:26,830 --> 00:22:30,160
Your Highness, rest assured. I will for surely look for Physician Zong.

279
00:22:30,160 --> 00:22:33,590
Eunuch Pan, you should do it properly.

280
00:22:33,590 --> 00:22:36,410
I will make sure I never mistreat you.

281
00:22:37,270 --> 00:22:41,420
Thank you for your support, Your Highness.

282
00:22:44,710 --> 00:22:48,120
Yu Liu, ask for Physician Zong now.

283
00:22:48,120 --> 00:22:50,970
Say that I am bloated and I have problems with regurgitation.

284
00:22:50,970 --> 00:22:55,430
I heard that Physician Zong's specialty is digestive organs. He's a professional. I particularly want him to come and take a look.

285
00:22:55,430 --> 00:22:58,260
Physician Zong and Consort Yang are related.

286
00:22:58,260 --> 00:23:01,370
He usually fawns on Prince Cao and Consort Yang, at the cost of his own life.

287
00:23:01,370 --> 00:23:04,720
Besides His Majesty, he only conducts medical examinations for Prince Cao and his mother.

288
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:08,170
Talented Lady, why do you insist on bringing him here?

289
00:23:08,170 --> 00:23:10,920
I am afraid I won't be able to convince him to accept the invitation.

290
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:13,530
It must be Physician Zong, and besides that, you have to be quick!

291
00:23:13,530 --> 00:23:17,030
You should say... that His Majesty said his medical skills were exquisite

292
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:20,400
and he recommended him to me. You should say it like this. This way he won't dare not come.

293
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:23,020
Yes. I will do exactly so.

294
00:23:29,690 --> 00:23:33,730
Crown Prince, I can only help you out up to this point.

295
00:23:33,730 --> 00:23:37,910
The rest... is in the hands of your Creator.

296
00:23:52,190 --> 00:23:55,590
- Where is Physician Zong?
- Talented Lady Wu has just developed a foul sickness.

297
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:58,740
She asked for him in the Hall of Sunset Pool.

298
00:24:02,260 --> 00:24:05,010
Your Majesty, the reason the Crown Prince's right arm is trembling

299
00:24:05,010 --> 00:24:07,880
is because he has been using his hands way too much and hurt his tendons.

300
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:10,190
I don't know what the reason is that His Highness overworked himself.

301
00:24:10,190 --> 00:24:13,600
I promise I will prescribe some proper medicine for him.

302
00:24:13,600 --> 00:24:16,960
The Crown Prince is very filial. He always prays and asks for my well-being.

303
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:18,940
He even spends the night transcribing fragments of the Confucian classics.

304
00:24:18,940 --> 00:24:21,030
Therefore, he overworked himself doing all of these.

305
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:26,310
Imperial Physician Jiang, is Crown Prince's arm severely injured?

306
00:24:26,310 --> 00:24:29,090
Your Majesty, filial piety is the highest virtue.

307
00:24:29,090 --> 00:24:31,250
Crown Prince's filial piety toward Your Majesty

308
00:24:31,250 --> 00:24:34,590
is really touching and exemplary to all the people.

309
00:24:34,590 --> 00:24:38,160
Your Majesty, please don't worry. Even though Crown Prince's arm is hurt,

310
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:40,450
but with good rest and nurturing,

311
00:24:40,450 --> 00:24:43,690
it will quickly recover.

312
00:24:46,180 --> 00:24:47,810
Go ahead and write the prescription.

313
00:24:47,810 --> 00:24:50,760
- Take good care of Crown Prince.
- Your edict is obeyed.

314
00:24:50,760 --> 00:24:54,790
Zhi'er, come here.

315
00:25:16,340 --> 00:25:21,200
Zhi'er, I wronged you today.

316
00:25:24,180 --> 00:25:27,600
They say, "The stronger the love, the harsher the scolding."

317
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:31,630
Imperial Father disciplined me for my sake.

318
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:35,690
It's good that you understand how I feel.

319
00:25:35,690 --> 00:25:40,790
Zhi'er, it's good that you pray for my blessing and copy the scriptures,

320
00:25:40,790 --> 00:25:45,610
but you should have told us sooner to avoid misunderstandings by the ministers.

321
00:25:45,610 --> 00:25:49,970
To pray for Your Majesty's blessing is based on my filial piety as your son and subordinate.

322
00:25:49,970 --> 00:25:53,990
Since it's filial piety, I don't need to publicize it and make Your Majesty worry.

323
00:25:53,990 --> 00:25:56,200
Whether Your Majesty knows,

324
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:58,460
whether all the people know,

325
00:25:58,460 --> 00:26:00,680
as long as it helps Your Majesty,

326
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:04,950
this son and subordinate will enjoy it no matter how tiring it is.

327
00:26:07,510 --> 00:26:10,600
Crown Prince pledged such an oath to copy 100 times of the scriptures.

328
00:26:10,600 --> 00:26:14,370
This filial piety is truly touching.

329
00:26:14,370 --> 00:26:18,170
Did His Highness the Crown Prince really finish copying the scriptures 100 times during two days?

330
00:26:18,170 --> 00:26:19,880
Not yet.

331
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:25,460
Through today, I've only completed copying 88 times.

332
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:27,430
88 times?

333
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:29,900
I wonder if this younger brother will be lucky enough

334
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:32,980
to view the graceful bearing of the scriptures?

335
00:26:37,490 --> 00:26:42,220
This servant has already asked people to bring over the crown prince's copied scriptures.

336
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:44,570
Your Majesty, please view.

337
00:26:44,570 --> 00:26:49,190
Consort Yang. Prince of Cao. Please view.

338
00:26:49,190 --> 00:26:51,170
Submit them immediately.

339
00:26:51,170 --> 00:26:53,590
Your edict is obeyed!

340
00:28:37,390 --> 00:28:41,610
Announcing His Majesty's decree!

341
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:47,640
"Crown Prince Li Zhi, in praying for his father's blessing,

342
00:28:47,640 --> 00:28:51,330
copying scriptures 100 times as to forgetting meals and sleep,

343
00:28:51,330 --> 00:28:53,560
and hurting his right arm.

344
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:57,770
The sincerity of his filial piety is touching.

345
00:28:57,770 --> 00:29:02,310
Crown Prince is humble with his merits, persistent despite setbacks,

346
00:29:02,310 --> 00:29:04,850
has the demeanor of a wise person.

347
00:29:04,850 --> 00:29:08,440
I am very gratified.

348
00:29:08,440 --> 00:29:13,540
Today, I announce Crown Prince's gesture of filial piety to the public

349
00:29:13,540 --> 00:29:16,680
so that he is the role model for all the princes

350
00:29:16,680 --> 00:29:20,990
and sets the example for all the people."

351
00:29:20,990 --> 00:29:23,580
As stated.

352
00:29:23,580 --> 00:29:25,610
We will abide by the decree

353
00:29:25,610 --> 00:29:29,020
to follow Crown Prince as the role model.

354
00:29:37,340 --> 00:29:40,120
A'Ni, please let me explain.

355
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:43,590
A'Ni, slow down a little! A'Ni!

356
00:29:44,880 --> 00:29:47,160
A'Ni, wait for me!

357
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:49,440
A'Ni, let me explain!

358
00:29:49,440 --> 00:29:53,000
A'Ni! Open up the door!

359
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:56,590
A'Ni, I, Cao Wu swear that I only like you and no other.

360
00:29:56,590 --> 00:30:00,180
- I have never coveted secrets from some Attire Expert An...
- What's wrong?

361
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:02,150
- Look at him.
- ...so that you can use the secrets as dowry.

362
00:30:02,150 --> 00:30:04,820
That's my aunt's ideal, and it has nothing to do with me.

363
00:30:04,820 --> 00:30:06,680
A'Ni!

364
00:30:07,340 --> 00:30:09,610
A'Ni! You have to believe me!

365
00:30:09,610 --> 00:30:11,540
- I'm telling the truth.
- Don't.

366
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:13,180
If my auntie didn't discover today,

367
00:30:13,180 --> 00:30:16,070
I would have carried the Caoji sample dress to you to confess my heart.

368
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:20,030
I know that you really want to win at the Hu Merchants Conference.

369
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:23,880
To make you happy, I'm willing to let Caoji lose to you.

370
00:30:24,660 --> 00:30:28,390
- A'Ni! A'Ni!
- No wonder Ruyi Resist Dye is good.

371
00:30:28,390 --> 00:30:31,470
It's all thanks to Cao Wu then.

372
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:34,490
It turns out it was all your great contribution, Cao Wu.

373
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:37,990
Quit talking nonsense here.

374
00:30:37,990 --> 00:30:41,540
I want to rely on my own skills to take the orders from the Hu merchants.

375
00:30:41,540 --> 00:30:43,270
Those sneaky ways of yours

376
00:30:43,270 --> 00:30:44,940
are not up to my standard.

377
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:47,820
And I also have to tell you that I have never liked you!

378
00:30:47,820 --> 00:30:51,660
If you continue causing trouble like this, we won't even stay friends in the future!

379
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:58,250
- A'Ni!
- Girls are shy.

380
00:30:58,250 --> 00:31:01,490
Of course, she'll talk like this in front of people.

381
00:31:01,490 --> 00:31:04,920
You should go back. After she has vented, you can come to apologize.

382
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:06,530
Let's go then.

383
00:31:06,530 --> 00:31:08,420
- Go.
- I've seen it many times.

384
00:31:30,320 --> 00:31:34,890
A'Ni, Cao Wu is in fact the one you have on your mind!

385
00:31:35,460 --> 00:31:38,010
Not at all!

386
00:31:38,010 --> 00:31:41,730
Then this is one-sided love and you are not interested in him!

387
00:31:41,730 --> 00:31:43,900
How could I be interested in him?

388
00:31:43,900 --> 00:31:48,490
Didn't you hear the nonsense he was spilling in front of my door? How exasperating!

389
00:31:48,490 --> 00:31:52,920
If anyone who didn't know the situation had overheard him, what would people think of me?

390
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:55,540
Most likely he was doing that on purpose!

391
00:31:55,540 --> 00:31:59,280
He probably knows that I am most concerned about the reputation of Ruyi Resist Dye's Shop.

392
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:02,620
That's why he is helping his auntie to come and make a ruckus.

393
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:05,260
Concerned about reputation?

394
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:08,180
That's right. Why haven't I thought of this?

395
00:32:08,180 --> 00:32:09,980
What?

396
00:32:10,660 --> 00:32:13,640
I've thought of a way to deal with Pei Xingjian.

397
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:17,200
You are a business person and you particularly care about reputation.

398
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:21,340
Pei Xingjian is a student at the respected Simen College, and he is paid by the government.

399
00:32:21,340 --> 00:32:26,560
When I tell people that he secretly took someone else's property, his career will be over.

400
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:30,730
At that time, he will shout and cry to give me back my mother's things.

401
00:32:30,730 --> 00:32:32,780
You are right.

402
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:35,820
- How will you do it then?
- Since I know his weakness now,

403
00:32:35,820 --> 00:32:38,920
of course, I have to strike it hard, and not be softhearted.

404
00:33:11,100 --> 00:33:15,700
Liuli, you will for sure win with this surprise move!

405
00:33:15,700 --> 00:33:19,800
Previously, I already felt that this silk dress was missing something.

406
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:23,400
But I couldn't figure out where this problem was coming from.

407
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:26,200
Now that you've added this layer of silk gauze to the skirt,

408
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:29,200
not only does the original sense of opulent elegance still fully remain,

409
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:32,200
it even adds the beauty of nuanced inner spirit.

410
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:33,800
It is so ingenious!

411
00:33:33,800 --> 00:33:38,200
With this sample dress, I am even more confident in tomorrow's competition.

412
00:33:38,200 --> 00:33:40,800
A'Ni, it's your craft that made this dress beautiful.

413
00:33:40,800 --> 00:33:43,200
I am only adding flowers to the splendor.  (Adding to what is already beautiful)

414
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:46,400
This silk dress is beautiful for its glamorous elegance.

415
00:33:46,400 --> 00:33:50,000
It's too bad that the beauty is so direct that it seemed a bit flaunting.

416
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:54,500
That's why I just covered it with a light layer of silk gauze to making it even better.

417
00:34:02,650 --> 00:34:05,920
[Letter of Accusation]

418
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:10,390
What are you doing?

419
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,200
This letter of accusation is written in a sad manner.

420
00:34:13,200 --> 00:34:16,600
Of course, it needs to have some tears to suit it.

421
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:42,200
[Submitted by Crown Prince Li Zhi]

422
00:34:49,160 --> 00:34:51,010
This concubine is stupid.

423
00:34:51,900 --> 00:34:54,200
[Proposal to reform the imperial examination system]

424
00:34:54,200 --> 00:34:56,200
Isn't that the memorial from the crown prince?

425
00:34:56,200 --> 00:34:58,800
Bring it and I'll take a look.

426
00:34:58,800 --> 00:35:00,300
Yes.

427
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:17,400
[Proposal to reform the imperial examination system]

428
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:31,400
Previously, I was quite hesitant about reforming the imperial examination system.

429
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:34,300
Now that I've read Crown Prince's memorandum,

430
00:35:35,100 --> 00:35:39,000
I finally realized that emphasizing Imperial Scholars over Classics Comprehension

431
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:41,400
makes a lot of sense.

432
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:45,400
It can impact long-term planning for Great Tang.

433
00:35:45,400 --> 00:35:49,000
Crown Prince is intelligent and knowledgeable.

434
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:53,000
He is really worthy to be the first-born son between the late empress and me.

435
00:36:13,200 --> 00:36:14,800
Talented Lady,

436
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:18,000
I don't know if I can ask this question or not.

437
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,000
Just ask.

438
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:23,000
You don't have any friendship with Crown Prince or Prince of Cao.

439
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:26,400
Why are you helping Crown Prince?

440
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:29,400
Crown Prince has a kind nature and he speaks sincerely.

441
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:32,400
He has a grand aspiration but also cares about the people.

442
00:36:32,400 --> 00:36:35,500
When I see him, he reminds me of myself when I first entered the palace

443
00:36:35,500 --> 00:36:38,700
and didn't know how high the sky was or how deep the earth was. (Didn't know her limits to what she could do)

444
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:41,200
It's just that Crown Prince doesn't know it yet.

445
00:36:41,200 --> 00:36:43,200
Sometimes, to reach one's ideal,

446
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:46,400
it isn't enough to have aspirations.

447
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:48,700
It isn't enough at all.

448
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:53,400
I just couldn't bear to see Crown Prince

449
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:56,200
waste many years to finally comprehend this truth.

450
00:36:56,200 --> 00:37:00,300
Once he understands, it will be too late.

451
00:37:07,200 --> 00:37:11,000
[Simen College]

452
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:14,400
Good morning.
[Assembly Hall]

453
00:37:18,600 --> 00:37:20,100
Good morning.

454
00:37:23,370 --> 00:37:25,070
Good morning, everyone.

455
00:37:27,330 --> 00:37:28,780
Brother Pan.

456
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:31,000
Good morning.

457
00:37:31,700 --> 00:37:35,400
Brother Pei, you look so pleased. Has something good happened?

458
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,800
There is something good.

459
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:40,600
This is something wonderfully good to benefit Great Tang for a millennium.

460
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:41,800
Tell me about it.

461
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:43,600
Brother Pan, haven't you heard?

462
00:37:43,600 --> 00:37:45,800
His Highness the Crown Prince argued with reason

463
00:37:45,800 --> 00:37:49,000
in his memorandum, to state the pros and cons of the imperial examination system

464
00:37:49,000 --> 00:37:51,200
and explore how to reform it.

465
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:55,000
His Majesty has decided to treat the stubborn illness in the imperial examination system

466
00:37:55,000 --> 00:37:57,100
with strong medicine.

467
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:02,200
Of course, I've heard about such a big event.

468
00:38:02,200 --> 00:38:04,600
If the imperial examination system is changed,

469
00:38:04,600 --> 00:38:07,600
the mechanism involved in advancing political will also be reformed.

470
00:38:07,600 --> 00:38:10,400
This is the kind of big event where pulling one strand of hair can trigger movement in the entire body.

471
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:14,200
At Simen College, from the high of the Director of Studies to the low of the students,

472
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:16,700
countless people are worried over this issue.

473
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:19,000
By contrast, you are looking so pleased.

474
00:38:19,000 --> 00:38:21,700
You should be careful not to get into trouble.

475
00:38:21,700 --> 00:38:23,400
Pushing the reform of the imperial exam system

476
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:26,000
is an achievement for our current era that will benefit for a millennium.

477
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:28,000
This is just like going into the bones to eliminate a toxin.
(Curing disease from the root of the problem)

478
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:31,400
There are some people who are about to die and will fight the last battle. What is there to fear?

479
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:33,800
Besides, this is just one of the benefits.

480
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:36,060
The most important is that the crown prince

481
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:38,800
has far-reaching foresight and aspires to benefit the whole nation.

482
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:42,700
This is a fortune for Great Tang and a blessing for the people.

483
00:38:47,800 --> 00:38:50,400
I heard that Xue Xu was unsuccessful climbing high in connecting with Director of Studies Hongwen,

484
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:52,800
so he came wanting to be our Director of Studies.

485
00:38:52,800 --> 00:38:55,600
